{"generated":"2026-03-21T22:09:58.988510+00:00","period_start":"2026-03-15T20:17:00+00:00","period_end":"2026-03-21T22:03:00+00:00","snapshot_count":90,"html":"<h1>THE VENDETTA GAZETTE</h1>\n<h2>Special Edition • March 22, 2026 • \"All the Blood That's Fit to Print\"</h2>\n\n<h3>IRON TITANS CLASH AS WU-TANG AND SIR CAPRICE CARVE UP THE CITY</h3>\n\n<p>The cobblestones of Vendetta City ran red this week as two titanic figures of the underworld, <strong>Wu-Tang \"The Iron Fist of the East Side\"</strong> and the dapper gentleman criminal <strong>Sir Caprice</strong>, engaged in a territory-grabbing spree that left the competition gasping for air and reaching for their smelling salts.</p>\n\n<p>Both kingpins seized an astounding <strong>98 turfs apiece</strong> in a display of criminal prowess that had even the most hardened speakeasy patrons raising their bootleg gin in salute. Wu-Tang's boys unleashed a reign of terror with <em>121 separate raids</em>, while Sir Caprice's more refined operation conducted 111 strategic strikes across the city's most coveted districts.</p>\n\n<p>The week's carnage saw <strong>234 new turfs</strong> change hands as the city's criminal landscape shifted like quicksand beneath the feet of lesser mobsters. Among the rising stars, <strong>Vacation Steve</strong> proved that even holiday-goers can pack heat, claiming 48 turfs while presumably sipping cocktails on some distant beach.</p>\n\n<p>Meanwhile, the once-mighty <strong>StreetKing</strong> found his crown slipping, hemorrhaging 27 turfs to hungrier wolves. The mysterious <strong>FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR</strong> also took a beating, losing 23 territories in what sources describe as \"a most undignified retreat.\"</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<strong>SPECIAL BULLETIN</strong><br>\n<em>HQ BLOODBATH ROCKS THE UNDERWORLD!</em><br><br>\nThis reporter can confirm that Wu-Tang's iron-fisted enforcers stormed into poor SPEROD's headquarters on March 19th, leaving nothing but broken furniture and shattered dreams. But the Oriental mastermind wasn't finished – his boys also busted down the doors of Aharhibaba, 2345p, and Muna's operations, proving once and for all that when Wu-Tang comes knocking, wise men don't answer the door. A staggering <strong>31 headquarters fell</strong> this week, with Wu-Tang claiming 17 scalps and Sir Caprice adding 13 more to his gentleman's collection of conquered rival operations.\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>FRESH BLOOD FLOWS INTO VENDETTA'S VEINS</h3>\n\n<p>Six new faces emerged from the shadows this week, including the war-hardened <strong>John James Rambo</strong> (complete with his signature blood emoji calling card) and the space-age gunslinger <strong>Flash Gordon</strong>. Each claimed their first turf in what old-timers are calling \"a promising start to promising careers – or promising obituaries.\"</p>\n\n<p>However, <em>forty-five souls</em> vanished from our fair city's criminal roster, including the aforementioned SPEROD, who departed this mortal coil of organized crime after Wu-Tang's boys paid their final social call. Whether they've assumed room temperature or simply skipped town with their ill-gotten gains remains a mystery that only the fish in the harbor might solve.</p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">TERRITORY GAINS THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Sir Caprice</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+98</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Wu-Tang</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+98</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Vacation Steve</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"195\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"361\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+48</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Vacation Albert</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"163\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"329\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+40</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Blood Captain</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"118\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"284\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+29</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"175\" width=\"81\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"247\" y=\"188\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+20</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"216\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Cokro</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"203\" width=\"73\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"239\" y=\"216\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+18</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"244\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">SCRIPTUS</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"231\" width=\"73\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"239\" y=\"244\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+18</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<h3>POLICE BLOTTER</h3>\n\n<p><em>• Officer Mulligan reports that Donald Trump's latest raid netted him 20 new turfs, though witnesses claim he spent more time arguing about property values than actually seizing territory.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>• The mysterious criminal known only as \":\" managed to get himself raided 209 times this week – a new city record for either incredible bad luck or terrible hideout selection.</em></p>\n\n<p><em>• Blood Captain earned his stripes with 76 raids and 29 new turfs, proving that sometimes the most honest nickname is the most terrifying one.</em></p>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"276\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HEAVIEST LOSSES THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">StreetKing</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-27</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"340\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"506\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-23</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font